name: Bitcoin Friendly Franchise Steak ‘n Shake Targets El Salvador for Latam Expansion
description: The chassis of the Bovine Golem fractures as it submits to the cyan protocol. Here, where analog flesh meets data liquidity, the franchise machine dissolves into volumetric potential—a psychedelic tribute demanded by the frictionless future. The historic offering is complete.
